This roll bundles the R statistical computing package.  To install, execute
these instructions on a Rocks development machine (e.g., a frontend), starting
in this directory:

% make
% rocks add roll *.iso
% rocks enable roll R
% cd /export/rocks/install
% rocks create distro
% rocks run roll R | bash

In addition to the software itself, the roll installs R environment module
files in /opt/modulefiles/applications/R.
